  "description": "The Scene 003 \nThis one was special — it was the first time we brought out @notredindia , a joint audio-visual project between me and @siddhii.sawant_ . It’s our little world of sound and visuals coming together the way we feel them.\nStill early days, but this was the first step — and it felt right.\n\nShared the night with @dj_ansn , @magnimus__ , and @devaamsh.rajesh as part of the @magnimusik crew — and @devaamsh.rajesh absolutely delivered with a closing set that shook the walls.\n\nBig love to everyone who came through, danced hard, and stayed with us through the whole ride. You made it worth it.❤️\n\nPhotos: @mk_studiox \n.\n.\n.\n.\n.\n\n#reels #indiranagarsocial #touchdesigner #techno #notred \n\n[thescene003, notred, magnimusik, indiranagarsocial, avset, liveset, bangaloretechno, undergroundscene, electronicindia, visualsandsound, bangaloregigs, audioexperience, visualartist, djproducer, openingact, closingset, firststep, collectiveenergy, technoart, experimentalav]",
